title: 2 bedroom, 3rd Floor, Vaulted Ceilings, W/D in Unit!!
posting_body: ['Split 2 Bedroom 2 Bathroom with In Home Washer/Dryer!', 'This Floor Plan Features:', 'The bedrooms are separated by the living room and are approximately the same size.', 'This home features two separate bathrooms, and a washer/dryer in a common area within your home so everyone has access to it.', 'You are greeted by large open kitchen with a washer/dryer, full-size microwave, stove/oven, garbage disposal and refrigerator.', 'The balcony is large enough for furniture and boasts a fantastic view.', 'There’s tons of closet, cupboard and storage space in this home.', 'The rent includes HEAT, SEWER, TRASH and one stall in the underground HEATED parking!', 'At Greenfield, you are not only going to find a great floor plan that fits your needs - you will also find miles of outdoor trails through the Shady Oak nature preserve and indoor amenities to keep you active on those cold winter days.', "Want heated parking and a fitness center that doesn't require you to dress up?", 'We have it!', 'We also have a large party room to host your gatherings, tennis and basketball courts, a putting green, and both an indoor and outdoor pool.', "Hopkins Main Street, Eden Prairie Shopping Center, Ridgedale Mall, and Minnetonka's Shady Oak Beach are right nearby, along with quick access to Hwy 7, 62, & 494.", 'Check out our photos!', "You'll be impressed, and your friends will too!", '920 Feltl Court, Hopkins, MN 55343', 'Mon -
